    "description": "Kids land on a promising planet but so did dangerous Astro Balls!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/609919a305995c237599d9682eed98d9.avif?t=1692735205\" width=500 height=175 /></span><br><br>Lane defense genre is back with new twists and turns! Are you ready?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/496dc793e015bc3f1e48cd3f132303cf.poster.avif?t=1692735205\" width=500 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/496dc793e015bc3f1e48cd3f132303cf.webm?t=1692735205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/496dc793e015bc3f1e48cd3f132303cf.mp4?t=1692735205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Plant traps: Turret, Popcorn Machine, Bomb, Wall, Spikes, Moving Platform and Mystery Box<br></li><li>Buy even more traps with your Popcorn<br></li><li>Upgrade traps with update points!<br></li><li>Wave Rewards! Random prizes make each run different<br></li><li>Skill Cards: use stars to buy cards to customize your personal playstyle<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/78ebf0391617e5112d3e8f5c790dd6e9.poster.avif?t=1692735205\" width=500 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/78ebf0391617e5112d3e8f5c790dd6e9.webm?t=1692735205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/78ebf0391617e5112d3e8f5c790dd6e9.mp4?t=1692735205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Over 400 ferocious enemy variations: squishy and slimy Astro Balls, armored space drillers, <br>exploding enemies, and big bad worms. Contains farts!<br></li><li>Move the kid: choose which lane you defend.<br></li><li>Ultimates: Clean waves with Laser, Snowball and help of your buddies.<br></li><li>Customize your Kid: Hair, clothing colors, skin tone, boots, you name it. All F2P accessible.<br></li><li>Hilarious sounds and graphics<br></li><li>Hours of gameplay, post launch updates! Join in!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/eb2b6ba1a5175be6663461e6b61c9716.poster.avif?t=1692735205\" width=500 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/eb2b6ba1a5175be6663461e6b61c9716.webm?t=1692735205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728980/extras/eb2b6ba1a5175be6663461e6b61c9716.mp4?t=1692735205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game Modes</strong><br><br></li><li>Normal levels: collect Stars to progress your customizable Skill Cards build. Each level has pre-set board states and interesting enemy waves to tickle your brains. <br></li><li>Hard levels: Like normal levels, but LOT harder. Can you beat those?<br></li><li>Endless Mode. The waves. Do. Not. Stop.</li></ul><br><strong>Early Access plan</strong><br><br><strong>UPDATE 1</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Endless game optimization<br></li><li>New Endless game Wave Reward Cards<br></li><li>Achievement updates</li></ul><br><strong>UPDATE 2</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Level Builder early test<br></li><li>Achievement updates</li></ul><br><strong>UPDATE 3</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New Skill Cards<br></li><li>Full controller support<br></li><li>Shop optimization<br></li><li>Achievement updates</li></ul><br><strong>UPDATE 4</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Final version of Level Builder<br></li><li>Shared Levels<br></li><li>Localization</li></ul><br>Hotfixes and important updates are patched as needed and patch notes are gathered weekly. As we approach version 1.0 launch we might add to this Roadmap.",
